owns in Denmark]]\n[[Category:Viking Age populated places]]\n", "name_user": "J\u00e9eM84", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eTwin towns and consulates:cz", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aarhus"}
{"title_page": "Parisa Fitz-Henley", "text_new": "{{BLP sources|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox person\n| image         = \n| imagesize     =\n| caption       = \n| birth_date     =  {{birth date and age|1977|7|22}}\n| birth_place    = [[Kingston, Jamaica]]\n| nationality = American-Jamaican\n| birth_name     =\n| occupation    = Actress\n| years_active   = 2006\u2013present\n| spouse =\n| children =\n}}\n'''Parisa Fitz-Henley''' is a Jamaican-American actress best known for her role as Reva Connors in ''[[Jessica Jones (TV series)|Jessica Jones]]'' and ''[[Luke Cage (TV series)|Luke Cage]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/luke-cage-review-netflix/|title=\u2018Luke Cage\u2019 Review: Netflix Delivers the Hero We Need|last=Keene|first=Allison|publisher=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|date=September 7, 2016|accessdate=September 7, 2016|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6kLjyDNTG|archivedate=September 7, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://mcuexchange.com/luke-cage-cast-and-crew-throw-wrap-party-as-production-nears-end-on-season-one/|title=Luke Cage Cast And Crew Throw Wrap Party As Production Nears End On Season One|last=Kincaid|first=Rhiannon|publisher=MCU Exchange|date=March 14, 2016|accessdate=March 14, 2016|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6g0odGQYo|archivedate=March 14, 2016}}</ref> Since 2017, Fitz-Henley has starred in the [[NBC]] drama ''[[Midnight, Texas]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/midnight-texas-pilot-picked-up-series-nbc-1201755506|title='Midnight, Texas' Pilot Picked Up To Series By NBC - Deadline|author=Nellie Andreeva|work=Deadline|date=May 13, 2016|accessdate=July 18, 2017}}</ref>\n\n== Filmography ==\n\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n|2006\n|''[[Even Money (film)|Even Money]]''\n|Caribbean Woman\n| \n|-\n|2006\n|''Fist in the Eye''\n|Megan\n| \n|-\n|2007\n|''[[The Jane Austen Book Club (film)|The Jane Austen Book Club]]''\n|Corinne\n| \n|-\n|2009\n|''Knuck