lot\", \"Sick Beats\"\n|-\n| 2016\u20132018\n| ''[[Luke Cage (TV series)|Luke Cage]]''\n|Reva Connors\n| 4 episodes\n\n|-\n| 2017\u20132018\n| ''[[Midnight, Texas]]''\n|Fiji Cavanaugh\n| Series Regular\n|-\n| 2017\n|''[[The Girlfriend Experience (TV series)|The Girlfriend Experience]]''\n|N/A\n| Episodes: \"Living Like a Tornado\", \"Eggshells\"\n|-\n| 2018\n|''[[Falling Water (TV series)|Falling Water]]''\n| Christy\n|Episodes: \"Risk Assessment\", \"Nothing Personal\"\n|-\n|2018\n|''Harry & Meghan: A Royal Romance''\n|[[Meghan, Duchess of Sussex|Meghan Markle]]\n|Television film\n|-\n|2020\n|''[[The Sinner (TV series)|The Sinner]]''\n| Leela Burns\n| Series Regular (Season 3)\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{IMDb name|1406792}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fitz-Henley, Parisa}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:American television actresses]]\n[[Category:American film actresses]]\n[[Category:21st-century American actresses]]\n[[Category:1977 births]]\n[[Category:Jamaican emigrants to the United States]]\n[[Category:People from Kingston, Jamaica]]\n", "text_old": "{{BLP sources|date=April 2020}}\n{{BLP IMDb-only refimprove|date=February 2020}}\n{{Infobox person\n| image         = \n| imagesize     =\n| caption       = \n| birth_date     =  {{birth date and age|1977|7|22}}\n| birth_place    = [[Kingston, Jamaica]]\n| nationality = American-Jamaican\n| birth_name     =\n| occupation    = Actress\n| years_active   = 2006\u2013present\n| spouse =\n| children =\n}}\n'''Parisa Fitz-Henley''' is a Jamaican-American actress best known for her role as Reva Connors in ''[[Jessica Jones (TV series)|Jessica Jones]]'' and ''[[Luke Cage (TV series)|Luke Cage]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/luke-cage-review-netflix/|title=\u2018Luke Cage\u2019 Review: Netflix Delivers the Hero We Need|last=Keene|first=Allison|publisher=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|date=September 7, 2016|accessdate=September 7, 2016|archiveurl=https:/