{"title_page": "18th Golden Globe Awards", "text_new": "{{Infobox film awards\n| number = 18\n| award = Golden Globe Awards\n| image = \n| caption = \n| date = 16 March 1961\n| best_film_drama = '' Spartacus ''\n| best_film_comedy = '' The Apartment ''\n| best_film_musical = '' Song Without End ''\n| last = 17th\n| next = 19th\n}}\nThe '''18th [[Golden Globe Award]]s''', honoring the best in [[film]] for [[1960 in film|1960]] films, were held on March 16, 1961.\n\n==Winners and nominees==\n\n===Film===\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture \u2013 Drama|Best Film \u2013 Drama]]====\n''' ''[[Spartacus (film)|Spartacus]]'''''\n*''[[Elmer Gantry (film)|Elmer Gantry]]''\n*''[[Inherit the Wind (1960 film)|Inherit the Wind]]''\n*''[[Sons and Lovers (film)|Sons and Lovers]]''\n*''[[Sunrise at Campobello]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture \u2013 Musical or Comedy|Best Film \u2013 Comedy]]====\n''' ''[[The Apartment]]'''''\n*''[[The Facts of Life (film)|The Facts of Life]]''\n*''[[The Grass Is Greener]]''\n*''[[It Started in Naples]]''\n*''[[Our Man in Havana (film)|Our Man in Havana]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture \u2013 Musical or Comedy|Best Film \u2013 Musical]]====\n''' ''[[Song Without End]]'''''\n*''[[Bells Are Ringing (film)|Bells Are Ringing]]''\n*''[[Can-Can (film)|Can-Can]]''\n*''[[Let's Make Love]]''\n*''[[Pepe (film)|Pepe]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Actor \u2013 Motion Picture Drama|Best Actor \u2013 Drama]]====\n''' [[Burt Lancaster]] \u2013 ''[[Elmer Gantry (film)|Elmer Gantry]]'''''\n*[[Trevor Howard]] \u2013 ''[[Sons and Lovers (film)|Sons and Lovers]]''\n*[[Laurence Olivier]] \u2013 ''[[Spartacus (film)|Spartacus]]''\n*[[Dean Stockwell]] \u2013 ''[[Sons and Lovers (film)|Sons and Lovers]]''\n*[[Spencer Tracy]] \u2013 ''[[Inherit the Wind (1960 film)|Inherit the Wind]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Actress in a Motion Picture \u2013 Drama|Best Actress \u2013 Drama]]====\n''' [[Greer Garson]] \u2013 ''[[Sunrise at Campobello]]'''''\n*[[Doris Day]] \u2013 ''[[Midnight Lace]]''\n*[[Nancy Kwan]] \u2013 ''[[The World of Suzie Wong (film)|The World of Suzie Wong]]''\n*[[Jean Simmons]] \u2013 ''[[Elmer Gantry (film)|Elmer Gantry]]''\n*[[Elizabeth Taylor]] \u2013 ''[[BUtterfield 8]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Actor \u2013 Motion Picture Musical or Comedy|Best Actor \u2013 Comedy or Musical]]====\n''' [[Jack Lemmon]] \u2013 ''[[The Apartment]]'''''\n*[[Cantinflas]] \u2013 ''[[Pepe (film)|Pepe]]''\n*[[Dirk Bogarde]] \u2013 ''[[Song Without End]]''\n*[[Cary Grant]] \u2013 ''[[The Grass Is Greener]]''\n*[[Bob Hope]] \u2013 ''[[The Facts of Life (film)|The Facts of Life]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Actress \u2013 Motion Picture Comedy or Musical|Best Actress \u2013 Comedy or Musical]]====\n''' [[Shirley MacLaine]] \u2013 ''[[The Apartment]]'''''\n*[[Lucille Ball]] \u2013 ''[[The Facts of Life (film)|The Facts of Life]]''\n*[[Capucine]] \u2013 ''[[Song Without End]]''\n*[[Judy Holliday]] \u2013 ''[[Bells Are Ringing (film)|Bells Are Ringing]]''\n*[[Sophia Loren]] \u2013 ''[[It Started in Naples]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Motion Picture|Best Supporting Actor]]====\n''' [[Sal Mineo]] \u2013 ''[[Exodus (1960 film)|Exodus]]'''''\n*[[Lee Kinsolving]] \u2013 ''[[The Dark at the Top of the Stairs (film)|The Dark at the Top of the Stairs]]''\n*[[Ray Stricklyn]] \u2013 ''[[The Plunderers (1960 film)|The Plunderers]]''\n*[[Woody Strode]] \u2013 ''[[Spartacus (film)|Spartacus]]''\n*[[Peter Ustinov]] \u2013 ''[[Spartacus (film)|Spartacus]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Motion Picture|Best Supporting Actress]]====\n''' [[Janet Leigh]] \u2013 ''[[Psycho (1960 film)|Psycho]]'''''\n*[[Ina Balin]] \u2013 ''[[From the Terrace]]''\n*[[Shirley Jones]] \u2013 ''[[Elmer Gantry (film)|Elmer Gantry]]''\n*[[Shirley Knight]] \u2013 ''[[The Dark at the Top of the Stairs (film)|The Dark at the Top of the Stairs]]''\n*[[Mary Ure]] \u2013 ''[[Sons and Lovers (film)|Sons and Lovers]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Director|Best Director]]====\n''' [[Jack Cardiff]] \u2013 ''[[Sons and Lovers (film)|Sons and Lovers]]'''''\n*[[Richard Brooks]] \u2013 ''[[Elmer Gantry (film)|Elmer Gantry]]''\n*[[Stanley Kubrick]] \u2013 ''[[Spartacus (film)|Spartacus]]''\n*[[Billy Wilder]] \u2013 ''[[The Apartment]]''\n*[[Fred Zinnemann]] \u2013 ''[[The Sundowners (1960 film)|The Sundowners]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Original Score|Best Music, Original Score]]====\n'''[[Dimitri Tiomkin]]''' \u2013 '''''[[The Alamo (1960 film)|The Alamo]]'''''\n*[[Ernest Gold (composer)|Ernest Gold]] \u2013 ''[[Exodus (1960 film)|Exodus]]''\n*[[Johnny Green]] \u2013 ''[[Pepe (film)|Pepe]]''\n*[[Alex North]] \u2013 ''[[Spartacus (film)|Spartacus]]''\n*[[George Duning]] \u2013 ''[[The World of Suzie Wong (film)|The World of Suzie Wong]]''\n\n====Best Film to Promote International Understanding====\n'''''[[Hand in Hand (film)|Hand in Hand]]'''''\n*''[[Conspiracy of Hearts]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for New Star of the Year \u2013 Actor|Most Promising Newcomer \u2013 Male]]====\n'''[[Michael Callan]]'''<br />\n'''[[Mark Damon]]'''<br />\n'''[[Brett Halsey]]'''<br />\n* [[Peter Falk]]\n* [[David Janssen]]\n* [[Robert Vaughn]]\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for New Star of the Year \u2013 Actress|Most Promising Newcomer \u2013 Female]]====\n'''[[Ina Balin]]'''<br />\n'''[[Nancy Kwan]]'''<br />\n'''[[Hayley Mills]]'''<br />\n* [[Jill Haworth]]\n* [[Shirley Knight]]\n* [[Julie Newmar]]\n\n====Henrietta Award (World Film Favorite)====\n'''[[Tony Curtis]]'''<br />\n'''[[Rock Hudson]]'''<br />\n'''[[Gina Lollobrigida]]'''\n\n====Special Award====\n'''[[Cantinflas]]''' ''(For comedy)''<br />\n'''[[Stanley Kramer]]''' ''(For artistic integrity)''\n\n====Special Merit Award====\n'''''[[The Sundowners (1960 film)|The Sundowners]]'''''\n\n====Samuel Goldwyn Award====\n'''''[[The Trials of Oscar Wilde]]''''' (English-Language Foreign Film)<br />\n'''''[[La Verite (film)|La V\u00e9rit\u00e9]]''''' (France) (Foreign-Language Foreign Film)<br />\n'''''[[The Virgin Spring]]''''' (Sweden) (Foreign-Language Foreign Film)<br />\n*''[[Pote tin Kyriaki]]'' (Greece)\n\n====[[Golden Globe Cecil B. DeMille Award|Cecil B. DeMille Award]]====\n'''[[Fred Astaire]]'''\n\n==References==\n*[https://www.imdb.com/event/ev0000292/1961 IMdb 1961 Golden Globe Awards]\n{{Golden Globe Awards Chron}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Golden Globe Awards 018}}\n[[Category:Golden Globe Awards ceremonies|*018]]\n[[Category:1960 film awards]]\n[[Category:1960 television awards]]\n[[Category:March 1961 events]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox film awards\n| number = 18\n| award = Golden Globe Awards\n| image = \n| caption = \n| date = 16 March 1961\n| best_film_drama = '' Spartacus ''\n| best_film_comedy = '' The Apartment ''\n| best_film_musical = '' Song Without End ''\n| last = 17th\n| next = 19th\n}}\nThe '''18th [[Golden Globe Award]]s''', honoring the best in [[film]] for [[1960 in film|1960]] films, were held on March 16, 1961.\n\n==Winners and nominees==\n\n===Film===\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture \u2013 Drama|Best Film \u2013 Drama]]====\n''' ''[[Spartacus (film)|Spartacus]]''\n*''[[Elmer Gantry (film)|Elmer Gantry]]''\n*''[[Inherit the Wind (1960 film)|Inherit the Wind]]''\n*''[[Sons and Lovers (film)|Sons and Lovers]]''\n*''[[Sunrise at Campobello]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture \u2013 Musical or Comedy|Best Film \u2013 Comedy]]====\n''' ''[[The Apartment]]''\n*''[[The Facts of Life (film)|The Facts of Life]]''\n*''[[The Grass Is Greener]]''\n*''[[It Started in Naples]]''\n*''[[Our Man in Havana (film)|Our Man in Havana]]''\n\n====[[Golden Globe Award for Best Motion Picture \u2013 Musical or Comedy|Best Film \u2013 Musical]]====\n''' ''[[Song Without End]]''\n*''[[Bells Are Ringing (film)|Bells Are Ringing]]''\n*''[[Can-Can (film)|Can-Ca